defaultWe understand that t
defaulthe Environmental Audit Committee is launching a new inquiry on the prevention and management of the introduction and spread of invasive alien species.
default This response intends to examine one particular invasive species, Japanese Knotweed, in light of the following question raised in the terms of reference:
defaultQuestion 8: The case for any change in the law regarding invasive species
default. 
