defaultstitute of Chartered Surveyors 
defaulthas published guidance in relation to Japanese Kn
defaultotweed and residential property which
default encourages 
defaultvaluers
default/surveyors to “consider the implications of a Japanese Knotweed infestation on or near a dwelling”.  Whilst no specific guidance has been published in relation to commercial property, surveyors would typically have the same considerations.  
