default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe Council of Mortgage Lenders has stated that there is no blanket policy that prevents lenders from providing mortgages if Japanese Knotweed is identified.  However, 
defaultwe have seen statistics where
default Japanese Knotweed 
defaulthas been
default identified in a survey
default and m
defaultortgage lenders 
defaulthave taken the following actions
